MySQL for queue engine
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

settins.py::

    INSTALLED_APPS += ('djcelery','djkombu',) 
    import djcelery 
    djcelery.setup_loader() 
    BROKER_URL="django://" 

